    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elio</ex></expan> Valerino excepto<lb break="no" n="2"/>ri <expan><abbr>Impp</abbr><ex>eratorum</ex></expan> in officio memo<lb break="no" n="3"/>ri<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> qui aput <note>sic</note> civitatem <lb n="4"/>Nicomediensium fat<lb break="no" n="5"/>i munus complevit <lb n="6"/>vixsit <note>sic</note> annis XXXII et <del rend="erasure">VI</del> <lb n="7"/>me<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> Leontius vir <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>docen</abbr><ex>arius</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> et <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Salon</abbr><ex>itanorum</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>ex curatoribus eiusd<lb break="no" n="10"/>em civitatis filio dulc<lb break="no" n="11"/>issimo adque <note>sic</note> obsequ<lb break="no" n="12"/>entissimo pater infeli<lb break="no" n="13"/>x qui quod primo mihi <lb n="14"/>hoc facere debuerat e<lb break="no" n="15"/>go feci
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In 2 Teile gebrochen. Oberhalb der Inschrift Reliefdarstellung eines Mannes. Z. 6 steht auf Rasur. Buchstabe A mit spitz nach unten zeigender Querhaste. (B): AE 1961: Z. 7: Aurelius; Z. 14: pie facere.</p>
            </div>
